{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月初三|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 3일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 3''' is the 3rd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Events ==
* {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|676|ja|676|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - 神に新穀を捧げる{{ill|Sōshoku-sai|ja|相嘗祭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} を初めて挙行{{要出典|date=2021-04|qq=}} * {{ill|Ken'nin|ja|建仁|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|1203|ja|1203|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Unkei|ja|運慶|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} と{{ill|Kaikei|ja|快慶|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} が{{ill|Tōdai-ji|ja|東大寺|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 南大門の金剛力士像を完成させる * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 15|ja|11月15日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Sōmon ninbetsuchō|ja|宗門人別帳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} を廃止
== Births == * {{ill|Annin (era)|ja|安永 (元号)|lt=Annin|lt_ja=安永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 7th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1778|ja|1778|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Kuniyoshi Ikkan-sai|ja|国友一貫斎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Inventor|ja|発明家|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} （+ {{ill|1840|ja|1840|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1848|ja|1848|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ueno Riichi|ja|上野理一|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Asahi Shimbun|ja|朝日新聞|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 創業（+ {{ill|1919|ja|1919|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）
